videos.description: Temple's Quinton Rose pokes the ball away and takes it down the court for the dunk.
videos.headline: Quinton Rose comes up with the steal and slam

videos.description: Sterling Brown drives and dishes to Semi Ojeleye for the slam, and the foul for SMU.
videos.headline: Semi Ojeleye throws down the and-1 dunk

videos.description: Shake Milton connects with Jarrey Foster for the alley-oop dunk to give SMU a 20-15 lead.
videos.headline: Jarrey Foster finishes the alley-oop with a strong slam

videos.description: SMU'S Sterling Brown finds Jarrey Foster for an alley-oop dunk to give the Mustangs a 14-point lead.
videos.headline: Foster throws down his second alley-oop dunk on the night

videos.description: Temple's Shizz Alston Jr. connects with Quinton Rose for the long alley-oop slam.
videos.headline: Alston Jr. finds Rose with the long pass for the alley-oop
